title: Sandra Day O'Connor High School Prom Ticket (2014)
description:
You have been cordially invited to attend Prom 2014: The Great Escape
Join us on the third of May from seven to eleven o'clock in the evening at the Bentley Projects to experience a night beyond reality!

Directions:
1. Open PDF
2. Print image onto semi-thick white card stock paper
3. Cut the ticket with the dimensions 11.3cm x 5.6cm
4. With a black pen, write any number below 70 on the back of the ticket
5. Show up to the dance early to use the printed tickets!
